prompt:
What are some common mistakes people make when baking a cake?
Common mistakes include overmixing the batter, which can cause the cake to become dense and heavy; not checking if all ingredients have been properly measured and combined before starting to bake; not leveling off the top of the pan after filling it with batter, which can lead to uneven baking; and forgetting to set a timer or oven alarm, which can result in overbaking or underbaking.
